# Driver — Pipeline Methods (CompilerDriver extensions)
#
# Extracted from driver.spl. Contains CompilerDriver methods for:
# - JIT compilation (jit_compile_and_run)
# - SMF execution (execute_smf)
# - Borrow checking (borrow_check, format_borrow_error)
# - Async processing (process_async)
# - MIR optimization (optimize_mir)
# - AOP weaving (weave_aop)
# - Debug trace injection (apply_debug_trace)
# - Optimization config (get_optimization_config)

